                "invention-title": [
                    "Hydrogen storage tank arrangement structure of hydrogen energy aircraft and hydrogen energy aircraft",
                    "一种氢能源飞机储氢罐布置结构和氢能源飞机"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the field of hydrogen energy aircrafts, and particularly relates to a hydrogen energy aircraft hydrogen storage tank arrangement structure and a hydrogen energy aircraft.The hydrogen energy aircraft hydrogen storage tank arrangement structure comprises sliding rail frames and a plurality of vertical frames, the sliding rail frames are symmetrically distributed at the two ends of an aircraft body in the aircraft, the vertical frames are arranged on each pair, and an upper wall plate is movably connected with the vertical frames and detachably connected with the sliding rail frames; the device is used for realizing emergency disengagement. The sliding rail frame and the vertical frame are arranged and are structurally matched with the upper wall plate to jointly complete the separation behavior under the emergency condition, the sliding rail frame and the vertical frame are arranged above a passenger cabin and are symmetrically arranged along the left side and the right side, and when the hydrogen storage tank encounters an impact load of emergency landing, the hydrogen storage tank can fly out towards the two sides of a machine body along a supporting frame of the sliding rail frame through emergency separation; and the hydrogen storage tank is prevented from compressing the living space of passenger cabin members downwards, so that the safety of passengers is ensured."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于氢能源飞机领域，具体涉及一种氢能源飞机储氢罐布置结构和氢能源飞机，包括滑轨框和若干立框，滑轨框对称分布在飞机内部的机身两端，每一对上都设置有立框，上壁板与立框之间可动连接，与滑轨框之间可拆卸连接，用于实现应急脱离；通过滑轨框与立框的布置，并于上壁板在结构上形成配合，共同完成应急情况下的脱离行为，将其设置在客舱上方，沿左、右两侧对称布置，储氢罐在遇到应急着陆的冲击载荷时，可通过应急断离沿滑轨框的支框向机身的两侧飞出，避免了储氢罐向下压缩客舱成员的生存空间，从而保证乘客的安全。"
                }
            ]
